      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then one day the ceiling in the dining room crashed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And luckily the only casualty was a young boy whose finger was broken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, the headmaster really thought he'd have to make the government provide us with something more suitable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
